arts.ttl: Red Star Belgrade and Sturm Graz end 4-game losing runs in Champions League
arts.sum: Red Star Belgrade and Sturm Graz ended four-game losing runs in the Champions League to get their first points and wins on Wednesday. Sturm’s Danish forward Mika Biereth sealed the win in the 59th for just the second goal in the competition for the Austrian champion after five rounds.
